 black holes in\nthe framework of loop quantum gravity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Apr 2021 17:00:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 14 Jul 2021 07:55:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-15"}
