eds due to Lorentzian assumptions (Mack) or unverifiable\nEuclidean assumptions (OS theorem).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Apr 2021 18:00:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 Jul 2021 17:45:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-15"}
