ted cycle of length $l$ for each $l\\in \\{3,...,\n\\max\\{\\left(\\sum_{i\\in S} n_i\\right) + 1 \\colon S\\subset\\{1,..., k\\}\\text{ with\n}|S|=k-1\\}\\}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Apr 2021 19:25:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-07"}
