increases the computed accretion luminosities\nqualitatively in a similar manner as observed in the spectral evolution of Cyg\nX-3 for a moderate clumping volume filling factor and a compact star mass of a\nfew (2 - 3) solar masses.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Apr 2021 06:04:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-02"}
