ntally confirms that energy dissipation by induced\nturbulent water motion is an important mechanism for colliding ice floe fields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Apr 2021 09:10:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-07"}
