ped by a\npopulation-level trade-off between growth and heterogeneity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Apr 2021 15:31:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 7 Apr 2022 08:35:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-24"}
